{"ID":"20240213213054-5sbohzm","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240213213054-5sbohzm","title":"页面置换算法","updated":"20240215194156"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240213213109-3tegsqn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213109-3tegsqn","updated":"20240213213220"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"发生缺页中断的条件：内存已满，此时会交换磁盘内的数据"}]},{"ID":"20240213213054-53r55q1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213054-53r55q1","updated":"20240213213348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"页面置换算法的目标：尽量减少页面换入换出的次数"}]},{"ID":"20240213213724-ctfoun3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213724-ctfoun3","updated":"20240213213724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/image-20240213213724-ry5p654.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240213213905-gb811dn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213905-gb811dn","updated":"20240213213908"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"算法："}]},{"ID":"20240213213929-qr5witc","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240213213929-qr5witc","updated":"20240213213929"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 最佳置换算法(OPT)"}]},{"ID":"20240213213929-moi1r9k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213929-moi1r9k","updated":"20240213213930"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最佳(Optimal, OPT)置换算法所选择的被淘汰页面将是以后永不使用的，或者是在最长时间内不再被访问的页面,这样可以保证获得最低的缺页率。"}]},{"ID":"20240213213929-66u0g90","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213929-66u0g90","updated":"20240213213929"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但由于人们目前无法预知进程在内存下的若千页面中哪个是未来最长时间内不再被访问的，因而该算法无法实现。"}]},{"ID":"20240213213948-xo2a2c8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240213213948-xo2a2c8","updated":"20240213213948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"先进先出(FIFO)页面置换算法"}]},{"ID":"20240213213948-dr8q3ck","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213948-dr8q3ck","updated":"20240213213949"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"优先淘汰最早进入内存的页面，亦即在内存中驻留时间最久的页面。"}]},{"ID":"20240213213948-gnxbilf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213948-gnxbilf","updated":"20240213213949"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"该算法实现简单，只需把调入内存的页面根据先后次序链接成队列，设置一个指针总指向最早的页面。"}]},{"ID":"20240213213948-io9aadp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213213948-io9aadp","updated":"20240213213948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"但该算法与进程实际运行时的规律不适应，因为在进程中，有的页面经常被访问。"}]},{"ID":"20240213214020-a95y5n4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20240213214020-a95y5n4","updated":"20240213214020"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最近最久未使用(LRU)置换算法"}]},{"ID":"20240213214020-tu3hxsy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213214020-tu3hxsy","updated":"20240213214021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选择最近最长时间未访问过的页面予以淘汰，它认为过去一段时间内未访问过的页面，在最近的将来可能也不会被访问。"}]},{"ID":"20240213214020-5tz1776","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213214020-5tz1776","updated":"20240213214021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"该算法为每个页面设置一个访问字段，来记录页面自上次被访问以来所经历的时间，淘汰页面时选择现有页面中值最大的予以淘汰。"}]},{"ID":"20240213214020-m2ainsd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213214020-m2ainsd","updated":"20240213214021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"再对上面的实例釆用LRU算法进行页面置换，如图3-29所示。"}]},{"ID":"20240213214020-f6o2h4x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240213214020-f6o2h4x","updated":"20240213214021"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进程第一次对页面2访问时，将最近最久未被访问的页面7置换出去。然后访问页面3时，将最近最久未使用的页面1换出。"}]},{"ID":"20240215194156-cr20cqv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240215194156-cr20cqv"}}]}